INSTRUCTIONS

mongoimport \
  --uri "mongodb://localhost:27017/flairhq" \
  --collection rejectionReason \
  --jsonArray \
  --file flairhq-mongo/rejection-reasons-seed.json
The collection name is rejectionReason — that's what Spring Data MongoDB derives from the RejectionReason class name by default. Adjust the URI/database name if yours differs.



